            "compression": 43958,
            "mimeType": "text/html",
            "text": "\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<!doctype html>\n<html lang=\"uk\">\n  <head><!-- ✨🧞‍♂️✨ 2 -->\n    <title>AI Automation Engineer в Real Estate Bees – Djinni</title><meta charset=\"utf-8\">\n<meta http-equiv=\"x-ua-compatible\" content=\"ie=edge\">\n<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\">\n\n\n  \n\n  \n  <meta name=\"ahrefs-site-verification\" content=\"e3fb4f761d8fc47e3989aa951de60e8790deb948c9050a096c02e8c189ed4d54\">\n  <meta name=\"google-translate-customization\" content=\"43b319e88d47400c-2c58b02d438c987e-gbc703ae24e1d942c-9\"/>\n\n    \n  <meta name=\"description\" content=\"We are looking for a hands-on AI Automation Engineer to own, build, and optimize our entire marketing automation, lead routing, and Voice AI ecosystem.This...\">\n  <link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https://djinni.co/jobs/834173-ai-automation-engineer/\">\n  \n    <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n      {\"@context\": \"https://schema.org/\", \"@type\": \"JobPosting\", \"applicantLocationRequirements\": {\"@type\": \"AdministrativeArea\", \"address\": {\"@type\": \"PostalAddress\", \"addressCountry\": null, \"addressLocality\": null, \"addressRegion\": \"Europe\", \"postalCode\": null}}, \"category\": \"ML AI\", \"datePosted\": \"2026-06-26T15:16:13.513242\", \"description\": \"We are looking for a hands-on AI Automation Engineer to own, build, and optimize our entire marketing automation, lead routing, and Voice AI ecosystem.This is not a traditional software engineering role requiring complex coding from scratch. Instead, we need a technical builder who masterfully connects systems, designs bulletproof workflows, and leverages AI platforms to drive revenue and protect our lead quality.\\n \\nWhat ownership means here\\nYou own the GoHighLevel direction outright. You decide what to automate, how to structure workflows, which integrations to build, and in what order \\u2014 then you build them. You\\u0027re accountable for whether automations actually run, leads actually route, and the system actually scales. When something breaks, you fix it or escalate with a fix already in motion. We won\\u0027t hand you a ticket queue, and we won\\u0027t check your hours. We look at whether the system works and continues to improve.\\n \\nWhat you\\u0027ll own\\n\\u2022 The GHL Ecosystem: Full end-to-end ownership of our entire GoHighLevel environment.\\n\\u2022 Lead Verification Workflows: Designing strict quality gates to catch bad leads before they trigger refunds.\\n\\u2022 Financial Impact: Direct visibility into and influence over refund rates and revenue attribution.\\n\\u2022 Omnichannel Automation: Crafting workflows, automations, and customer journeys across all brands.\\n\\u2022 Voice AI Agents: Configuring and optimizing conversational flows using platforms like Vapi, Bland, or Retell.\\n\\u2022 System Integrations: Building and maintaining webhooks, API integrations, and third-party connections.\\n\\u2022 Stack Optimization: Deciding which tools GHL should absorb and confidently retiring the rest.\\n \\nWhat we are looking for\\nHighLevel Mastery: Deep, hands-on experience with GoHighLevel (or equivalent platforms like ActiveCampaign).\\nVoice AI Configuration: Experience setting up and fine-tuning conversational AI platforms (Vapi, Bland, Retell, etc.).\\nIntegration Expertise: Strong skills with Make.com, Zapier, or basic custom code for API webhooks and data routing.\\nData \\u0026 Logic Driven: Ability to map out complex lead routing logic and ensure seamless data synchronization.\\nCompliance-Aware: A solid understanding of compliance (TCPA, GDPR, carrier guidelines) at a practical \\\"don\\u0027t break the rules\\\" level.\\n \\nWhat you get\\n\\u2022 Direct Impact: Visible, measurable impact on revenue\\u2014not abstract contributions.\\n\\u2022 No Bureaucracy: Work with a team that ships fast, values execution, and skips corporate red tape.\\n\\u2022 Leadership Alignment: A direct line to leadership with full visibility into business metrics.\\n\", \"directApply\": true, \"employmentType\": \"FULL_TIME\", \"experienceRequirements\": {\"@type\": \"OccupationalExperienceRequirements\", \"monthsOfExperience\": 24.0}, \"hiringOrganization\": {\"@type\": \"Organization\", \"name\": \"Real Estate Bees\", \"sameAs\": \"https://realestatebees.com/\"}, \"identifier\": 834173, \"industry\": \"proptech\", \"jobLocationType\": \"TELECOMMUTE\", \"title\": \"AI Automation Engineer\", \"url\": \"https://djinni.co/jobs/834173-ai-automation-engineer/\", \"validThrough\": \"2026-07-26T15:16:13.513242\"}\n    </script>\n  \n\n\n    \n  \n  \n    \n  \n\n  <meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"article\" />\n  <meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"AI Automation Engineer в Real Estate Bees \" />\n  <meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"We are looking for a hands-on AI Automation Engineer to own, build, and optimize our entire marketing automation, lead routing, and Voice AI ecosystem.This is not a traditional software...\" />\n  <meta property=\"og:url\" content=\"https://djinni.co/jobs/834173-ai-automation-engineer/\" />\n  <meta property=\"og:image\" content=\"https://p.djinni.co/c4/dd1e527973c4c6bda385df629c87de/images_400.png\">\n  <meta name=\"twitter:card\" content=\"summary\" />\n  <meta name=\"twitter:description\" content=\"We are looking for a hands-on AI Automation Engineer to own, build, and optimize our entire marketing automation, lead routing, and Voice AI ecosystem.This is not a traditional software...\" />\n  <meta name=\"twitter:title\" content=\"AI Automation Engineer в Real Estate Bees \" />\n  <meta name=\"twitter:image\" content=\"https://p.djinni.co/c4/dd1e527973c4c6bda385df629c87de/images_400.png\">\n<meta name=\"application-name\" content=\"&nbsp;\"/>\n<meta name=\"msapplication-TileColor\" content=\"#4859FF\" />\n<link rel=\"manifest\" href=\"/static/manifest.json\" />\n<meta name=\"msapplication-square310x310logo\" content=\"/static